Name: Me
Message: Hey Maya, it's Andrew Konoff from okcupid. How's your long weekend been?

Name: Maya
Message: Hey! It's been lovely -- cottage, friends, family, food. No complaints.  How about you?

Name: Maya
Message: Were you in town or have you started traveling around?

Name: Me
Message: That sounds rad. I had something similar - been in Regina since last Thursday, and it has been super quiet and relaxing here.

Name: Me
Message: I fly back tomorrow and will definitely miss the calm. Not the mosquitoes though. Won't be missing them.

Name: Me
Message: Where were you cottaging? I’m gonna make that a verb if it isn’t already.

Name: Maya
Message: Having never been to Regina I feel like 'quiet' and 'relaxing' are probably accurate descriptors. My best friend has a place on lake muskoka, a tiny little cabin amongst disgusting monster cottages.  It was gorgeous but yes very many Mosquitos SO MANY

Name: Me
Message: They're the worst. Pretty sure I need a blood transfusion. And I think that's where I went to a cottage the other month. Super beautiful sunsets, super unaffordable real estate.

Name: Me
Message: I actually have to get supper ready for the fam - but I wanted to find out what you're up to on Friday. There's a rum bar near my new hood that I think we'd have fun at. Say 8:30pm?

Name: Maya
Message: I would absolutely love to but unfortunately can't on Friday -- you free any other days this week?

Name: Maya
Message: Like Wednesday. Would you be free Wednesday?

Name: Me
Message: Unfortunately I've gotta meet someone for businessy stuff that night. Thursday, Saturday or Sunday evening I'm free too!

Name: Maya
Message: What about Thursday then?

Name: Me
Message: Heck yeah. 8:30 work for ya?

Name: Maya
Message: Yupppp that should be fine!

Name: Me
Message: Awesome. 8:30 at Rhum Corner. See you in a couple days

Name: Maya
Message: Hey Andrew I am so sorry but I'm going to have to reschedule tomorrow evening, there's a lab seminar that my boss has just very strongly "suggested" I attend.  Is there any way we could do another day instead? I really am sorry this is so last minute

Name: Me
Message: Ah that sucks! Oddly enough, my bud tonight had cancelled on me like 45 minutes ago so that would have worked perfectly

Name: Me
Message: I'm free Sunday though - and actually next week is way open for me. What's your schedule looking like?

Name: Maya
Message: Ok awesome Sunday is good as is every night next week except for Thursday! So your pick!

Name: Me
Message: Lets do some Sunday drinking, like responsible adults. Same time and place?

Name: Maya
Message: Done deal

Name: Maya
Message: Still good for tonight?

Name: Me
Message: Was just about to message you. Absolutely. I'm looking forward to it.

Name: Maya
Message: Hey Andrew I might be a couple of minutes transportation's been giving me issues

Name: Me
Message: No worries - thanks for letting me know! Btw just so you recognize me, I'm the guy with the fedora and neckbeard

Name: Maya
Message: I feel like that won't be such a distinguishing feature around Bellwoods but I'm always up for a challenge

Name: Me
Message: I guess I should have brought my skateboard, hey?

Name: Maya
Message: Oh god

Name: Maya
Message: Hey Andrew I meant to message you earlier but the week got away from me, I had a good time on Sunday. In spite of your rather unfortunate proclivity for skateboards.

Name: Me
Message: Hey! Glad I could overcome that strike against me. I was actually convinced I wouldn’t hear from you. Thought something was the matter. Was I just reading you wrong?

Name: Maya
Message: Yeah, no nothing was wrong I think I was just tired and starting to think about work which is rarely a good combination. Totally see how I could have given you that impression. Didn't mean to!

Name: Me
Message: Oh don't even worry about it! I just wanted to be sure you were ok. I had a good time too that night. How's your week been? Pretty work intensive?

Name: Maya
Message: It's been good. Busy. But good. How about you? Any crazy app developments? Figured out the exact number of beats per minute that corresponds to the dancing twins emoticon?

Name: Me
Message: Same. Super hectic. I’m outsourcing the dancing twin emoji analysis to a research group at MIT, I suspect they may be able to crack the pattern

Name: Me
Message: but don’t hold your breath. It’s a toughie.

Name: Maya
Message: Oh good, I really do feel it's best left to the experts. I know it's a lot to hope for though. Hoped and expectations will be managed accordingly.

Name: Me
Message: :) you know, this next little while is gonna be mad busy for me, but I think we should try to get a bite to eat. If not this coming week, the one after.

Name: Maya
Message: Sounds good

Name: Maya
Message: I just walked past your place

Name: Maya
Message: Not in a creepy stalker way. I was really casual.

Name: Me
Message: That's crazy! I just walked in my place.

Name: Maya
Message: Maaaan if i had been just 8 hours later .... so close

Name: Maya
Message: You free for dinner Wednesday by any chance?

Name: Me
Message: I'm up at a cottage then. Back on Sunday. Will hopefully be less exhausted then!

Name: Me
Message: Where were you thinking? Hummus paradise?

Name: Maya
Message: I'm jealous.  As much as I would love to do Ezra's pound-turned-hummuseria I'm pretty sure it closes super early.  I've been craving utopia lately though if you're down

Name: Me
Message: Utopia? I have never heard of it

Name: Maya
Message: It's at college + Clinton. Endorsed by Rachel McAdams and Ryan Gosling in case that's convincing. Also down to go someplace else if you have something in mind

Name: Me
Message: No, that sounds awesome! How about I throw you a text on Sunday and we can see what day works?

Name: Maya
Message: Yeah sounds good
